        "content": "<p>rvolosatovs created <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/pull/12174#discussion_r2827396316\">PR review comment</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>That would be awesome!</p>\n</blockquote>",
